  "title": "feat(index): add story [PART-3]",
  "body": "This PR adds a minimal story to work on the `index` widget. We can review the design later, right now it's mostly to be able to have a playground to work on. The current feature set is limited to only display a static list of hits (it trigger the correct number of requests). We only take into account the local `helper` of the `index` which means that parent widgets are ignored. We'll cover that soon.\r\n\r\n~~**Currently the story does not work because the previous branches are not correctly rebased.**~~\r\n\r\n> https://deploy-preview-3914--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories/?path=/story/index--default",
